>Notice: Narrowband HD supports only H.264/H.265 formats, only yuv420p, 8-bit depth, and does not support multi-target video transcoding output or video concatenation. For more information, see [Narrowband HD overview](https://help.aliyun.com/document_detail/2984556.html).', example='0'),
  }(name='TranscodeVideo', description='The video transcoding parameters. An empty value indicates that video processing is disabled and the output file does not contain a video stream.

